Git repo for system programming cohort 2017 team 3 project work

Build:
make all

Use:
./server
./client <ip> <group-id> <message>

press Ctrl+C to exit server

Example:

Client:
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 0 "message from client"
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 0 "message from client1"
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 10 "message from client"
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 10 "message from client1"
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 3 "message from client"
sgr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./client 127.0.0.1 3 "message from client1"

Server:
gr@ubuntu:~/sgr/sysprog-team3$ ./server 
SERVER started at port: 5000



